{"tid":1992984,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］話說老豆啱先買大家樂外賣","createTime":"2020-04-28T12:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T07:12:28.000Z","uid":100155,"like":87,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b62204db43ee557dbea33009870e37679b6b7f14","tid":1992984,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"佢買左咕嚕肉飯，一打開蓋，發現：「仆街，得三粒肉嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqDTmw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqDTmw9.png&h=770a778d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你以為舊肉都唔細? Sorry肉中間係一大舊骨黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而老母買左個唔知咩牛肉炒飯之類，不過啲肉少到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加埋應該有一隻手指咁大（sor有d濛，我一路笑一路影）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsEg9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsEg9a.png&h=769f8b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣做生意，快d執7左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc99bf83ca583b4b9fbe3ea523d421c0c52ea1f","tid":1992984,"uid":100155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:50:29.000Z","msg":"今集鏗鏘集回顧警暴，受害人投訴無門，竟然冇人推上熱門 ?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d71ac63dec2877cf0873d6a38ea4c2f596abf397","tid":1992984,"uid":69159,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"有時可能係為方便 唔想諗先幫襯大家樂<br />\n你試下去黃店買外賣<br />\n拆左個包裝<br />\n佢就會話好食 問你邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=